input.description: The name of the adapter. Default Name: NetAppActor
The version of the NetApp DFM application. Supported version is: v4.0

Supported item types are:
1. find-dataset 2. find-dataset-members 3. find-protection-policy 4. find-provisioning-policy 5. find-resource-pool 6. find-resource-pool-members 7. find-job-status 8. find-aggregate 9. find-volume 10. find-storage-service 11. find-storage-service-datasets 12. find-custom-field 13. find-custom-field-values 14. find-vfiler 15. find-lun 16. find-filer 17. find-host 18.find-aggregate-details 19.find-vfiler-template 20. find-job-events 21. find-igroup 22. find-lun-mapped-to-igroup

Appropriate Items XML for the request that needs to be executed depending upon the item type.
For ex. If Find Resource Pool needs to be executed sample items XML would be:
<items> <item> <object-name-or-id>bmc-aggr0</object-name-or-id> <resource-tag>test</resource-tag> <check-licenses>nfs</check-licenses> <include-free-space>true</include-free-space> <controller-failure>true</controller-failure> <disk-failure>single</disk-failure> <sub-system-failure>true</sub-system-failure> </item> </items>
